dc_title_s: A Plan of the attack of Fort Sulivan, the key of Charlestown, in South Carolina, on the 28th. of June 1776. By His Majesty's squadron, commanded by Sir Peter Parker
dc_description_s: Oriented with north to the right. British squadron represented pictorially. In lower margin: The following description of the attack of Fort Sulivan, was received in a letter from Sir Peter Parker to Mr. Stephens, Secretary of the Admiralty.
dc_publisher_s: London, Printed for Robt. Sayer & Jno. Bennett, 1776.
dc_subject_sm: Fort Moultrie, Battle of, S.C., 1776—Maps, Manuscript—Early works to 1800
